{"url": "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/04/16/prince-harry-sought-counselling-death-mother-led-two-years-total/", "text": "Prince Harry has disclosed that he sought counselling after enduring two years of \u201ctotal chaos\u201d while still struggling in his late twenties to come to terms with the death of his mother.\n\nThe Prince says in an interview with The Telegraph that he \u201cshut down all his emotions\u201d for almost two decades after losing his mother, Diana, Princess of Wales, despite his brother, Prince William, trying to persuade him to seek help.\n\nDisclosing that he has spoken to a professional about his mental health, he describes how he only began to address his grief when he was 28 after feeling \u201con the verge of punching someone\u201d and facing anxiety during royal engagements.", "images": ["https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/briefs/2025/11/20/TELEMMGLPICT000444325789_17636460636420_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqW-Lc0TAiyYzC8hrrx9reNP4Xpit_DMGvdp2n7FDd82k.jpeg?imwidth=350", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/etc.clientlibs/settings/wcm/designs/telegraph/core/clientlibs/ui/dist/static/resources/images/flags/USA-SVG.svg", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/briefs/2025/11/20/TELEMMGLPICT000322383991_17636440767070_trans_NvBQzQNjv4Bq3Z7i_2nUjuO-XXgVmfiyhFHmPOpeFd0SyQx9dn7kM_w.jpeg?imwidth=350", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/Author%20photos/hannah-furness-xlarge.png?imwidth=100", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/news/2017/04/16/TELEMMGLPICT000118936558_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqPuL-8ex6Wxr3HGFUi6PIc5XLXiVyP9u62yFpPEk2K00.jpeg?imwidth=350", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/briefs/2025/11/20/TELEMMGLPICT000449813729_17636447438980_trans_NvBQzQNjv4Bq2xkU7tgIOCwaluShULzvOGQnZJIETfWB_fUbKb77n0w.jpeg?imwidth=350", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/briefs/2025/11/20/TELEMMGLPICT000448734736_17636457925080_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqI0P8f9bO4E3qjnGDTmoejRLcrmo1mhLKr08jNmJN5TQ.jpeg?imwidth=350", "https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/